    <p style="font-family: '굴림'; font-weight: bold;">6. 일반공문서의 관리</p>
    
    <p style="font-family: '굴림';"><br></p>

    <p style="margin-left: 27.7pt; text-indent: -27.7pt; font-family: '굴림';">
