<P CLASS=HStyle24 STYLE='margin-left:1.4pt;text-indent:-1.4pt;line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3.1.1 고객만족도 조사 계획을 승인한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle24 STYLE='margin-left:1.4pt;text-indent:-1.4pt;line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3.1.2 고객만족도 조사 단위별 조사계획을 승인한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle24 STYLE='margin-left:1.4pt;text-indent:-1.4pt;line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3.1.3 고객만족도 조사 결과를 검토한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle24 STYLE='margin-left:1.4pt;text-indent:-1.4pt;line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3.1.4 고객만족도 조사 대책수립을 검토 및 승인한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle24 STYLE='margin-left:1.4pt;text-indent:-1.4pt;line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></P>

