<P CLASS=HStyle24 STYLE='margin-left:1.4pt;text-indent:-1.4pt;line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3.2.1 고객 만족도 조사계획을 수립한다..</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle24 STYLE='margin-left:1.4pt;text-indent:-1.4pt;line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3.2.2 설문지를 확정하고 고객만족도 설문지를 작성한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle24 STYLE='margin-left:1.4pt;text-indent:-1.4pt;line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3.2.3 분석방법을 결정한다.</SPAN></P>

