<P CLASS=HStyle24 STYLE='margin-left:1.4pt;text-indent:-1.4pt;line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3.3.2 설문조사시 문제점을 파악한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle24 STYLE='margin-left:1.4pt;text-indent:-1.4pt;line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3.3.3 의견을 제시한다.</SPAN></P>

